data.name: menuItemAddTab.ToolTipText
data.value: Adds 1 blank tab page to the programs tab control

data.name: menuItemCloseAllButCurrent.ToolTipText
data.value: Closes all but the active tab page

data.name: menuItemCloseAndDelete.ToolTipText
data.value: The program will close the active file and then attempt to delete the file

data.name: menuItemSignature.ToolTipText
data.value: Inserts a signature at the end of the document. The default signature is your user name but you may change this in the preference panel

data.name: menuItemAutoIndent.ToolTipText
data.value: When checked, attempts to keep the amount of tabs at the start of lines the same. Word wrap must be off for you to use this feature

data.name: menuItemRegexRefactoring.ToolTipText
data.value: Opens a dialog for refactoring the current text using regex profiles
